ocabulary is small and stable; per-hub regex per domain is the distributed monolith in another shape\",\"evidence\":\"iterations/iteration-001.md#negative-knowledge\"}],\"timestamp\":\"2026-07-18T06:08:00Z\",\"durationMs\":480000,\"executor\":{\"kind\":\"cli-opencode\",\"model\":\"zai-coding-plan/glm-5.2\",\"lineage\":\"glm-oob\"},\"graphEvents\":[{\"type\":\"node\",\"id\":\"q1\",\"kind\":\"QUESTION\",\"label\":\"If Layer-1 routing were deleted entirely, what breaks vs improves?\"},{\"type\":\"node\",\"id\":\"f1-precedent\",\"kind\":\"FINDING\",\"label\":\"_apply_deep_skill_routing_layer is the one shipped precedent and is non-generalizable\"},{\"type\":\"node\",\"id\":\"f4-reframe\",\"kind\":\"CLAIM\",\"label\":\"Abolition is a tier-split (cold advisor + hot advisor-loaded vocab), not a deletion\"},{\"type\":\"edge\",\"id\":\"e-q1-f1\",\"source\":\"f1-precedent\",\"target\":\"q1\",\"relation\":\"ANSWERS\"},{\"type\":\"edge\",\"id\":\"e-f1-f4\",\"source\":\"f4-reframe\",\"target\":\"f1-precedent\",\"relation\":\"DERIVED_FROM\"}]}\nEOF\necho \"appended iter 1 to state.jsonl\"","time":{"start":1784347765568,"end":1784347765569}},"id":"prt_f736a2b34001P8570NleFYCAfx","sessionID":"ses_08c9e6f24ffeeO094AtRujB8OZ","messageID":"msg_f7369c98a001q7XA0BToR473W8"}}
