-knowledge\"}],\"timestamp\":\"2026-07-18T06:18:00Z\",\"durationMs\":540000,\"executor\":{\"kind\":\"cli-opencode\",\"model\":\"zai-coding-plan/glm-5.2\",\"lineage\":\"glm-oob\"},\"graphEvents\":[{\"type\":\"node\",\"id\":\"q2\",\"kind\":\"QUESTION\",\"label\":\"Which routing primitive transfers from a non-routing domain, and at what cost?\"},{\"type\":\"node\",\"id\":\"f2-health\",\"kind\":\"CLAIM\",\"label\":\"Each mode has a runtime health score; weights adapt (load-balancer transfer)\"},{\"type\":\"node\",\"id\":\"f4-feedback\",\"kind\":\"FINDING\",\"label\":\"The genuine transfer is the feedback channel itself (closed-loop routing), smaller than health-check\"},{\"type\":\"node\",\"id\":\"f5-reframe\",\"kind\":\"CLAIM\",\"label\":\"Closed-loop routing supplies the measurement infrastructure run-2 said was missing\"},{\"type\":\"edge\",\"id\":\"e-q2-f4\",\"source\":\"f4-feedback\",\"target\":\"q2\",\"relation\":\"ANSWERS\"},{\"type\":\"edge\",\"id\":\"e-f2-f4\",\"source\":\"f4-feedback\",\"target\":\"f2-health\",\"relation\":\"SUPERSEDES\"},{\"type\":\"edge\",\"id\":\"e-f4-f5\",\"source\":\"f5-reframe\",\"target\":\"f4-feedback\",\"relation\":\"DERIVED_FROM\"}]}\nEOF\necho \"appended iter 2\"","workdir":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.worktrees/0063-skilled-router-collapse"},"output":"appended iter 2\n","metadata":{"output":"appended iter 2\n","exit":0,"truncated":false},"title":"cat >> .opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/023-oob-glm-parallel/research/lineages/glm-oob/deep-research-state.jsonl <<'EOF'\n{\"type\":\"iteration\",\"iteration\":2,\"mode\":\"research\",\"target_agent\":\"deep-research\",\"agent_definition_loaded\":true,\"resolved_route\":\"Resolved route: mode=research target_agent=deep-research\",\"newInfoRatio\":0.80,\"status\":\"insight\",\"focus\":\"Cross-domain analogies — load-balancer health-check transfer (agenda #3): survey 5 analogies, find the one primitive routing lacks\",\"findingsCount\":5,\"keyQuestions\":[\"q2\"],\"answeredQuestions\":[\"q2\"],\"noveltyJustification\":\"F4 (feedback channel as the genuine transfer, smaller than health-check) and F5 (closed-loop re-frames run-2 measurement gap) are net-new; the four collapse-to-existing findings are confirmatory\",\"ruledOut\":[{\"approach\":\"OS scheduler priority/preemption as a routing primitive\",\"reason\":\"Priority=today's weight; preemption is incoherent for one-shot routing; aging collapses to learned weights\",\"evidence\":\"iterations/iteration-002.md#negative-knowledge\"},{\"approach\":\"IP longest-prefix match as a routing primitive\",\"reason\":\"vocabularyClasses already is longest-prefix match by another name\",\"evidence\":\"iterations/iteration-002.md#negative-knowledge\"},{\"approach\":\"Receptionist ask-don't-guess as a routing primitive\",\"reason\":\"Already shipped as defer; triage protocol is bundleRules\",\"evidence\":\"iterations/iteration-002.md#negative-knowledge\"},{\"approach\":\"Full health-score routing (F2) as immediate destination\",\"reason\":\"F3 four costs (state-space explosion, grader cost, cold-start, Goodhart) make it multi-release, not refactor\",\"evidence\":\"iterations/iteration-002.md#negative-knowledge\"}],\"timestamp\":\"2026-07-18T06:18:00Z\",\"durationMs\":540000,\"executor\":{\"kind\":\"cli-opencode\",\"model\":\"zai-coding-plan/glm-5.2\",\"lineage\":\"glm-oob\"},\"graphEvents\":[{\"type\":\"node\",\"id\":\"q2\",\"kind\":\"QUESTION\",\"label\":\"Which routing primitive transfers from a non-routing domain, and at what cost?\"},{\"type\":\"node\",\"id\":\"f2-health\",\"kind\":\"CLAIM\",\"label\":\"Each mode has a runtime health score; weights adapt (load-balancer transfer)\"},{\"type\":\"node\",\"id\":\"f4-feedback\",\"kind\":\"FINDING\",\"label\":\"The genuine transfer is the feedback channel itself (closed-loop routing), smaller than health-check\"},{\"type\":\"node\",\"id\":\"f5-reframe\",\"kind\":\"CLAIM\",\"label\":\"Closed-loop routing supplies the measurement infrastructure run-2 said was missing\"},{\"type\":\"edge\",\"id\":\"e-q2-f4\",\"source\":\"f4-feedback\",\"target\":\"q2\",\"relation\":\"ANSWERS\"},{\"type\":\"edge\",\"id\":\"e-f2-f4\",\"source\":\"f4-feedback\",\"target\":\"f2-health\",\"relation\":\"SUPERSEDES\"},{\"type\":\"edge\",\"id\":\"e-f4-f5\",\"source\":\"f5-reframe\",\"target\":\"f4-feedback\",\"relation\":\"DERIVED_FROM\"}]}\nEOF\necho \"appended iter 2\"","time":{"start":1784347946498,"end":1784347946499}},"id":"prt_f736cedf4001WRSmV9Rf5nY3u2","sessionID":"ses_08c9e6f24ffeeO094AtRujB8OZ","messageID":"msg_f736ca5e00018BFAc3ArUPjlXc"}}
