TION\",\"label\":\"Does confidence-first + learned routing make defaultMode meaningless?\"},{\"type\":\"node\",\"id\":\"f3-learn-assignment\",\"kind\":\"FINDING\",\"label\":\"Learn the vocabulary-to-mode assignment, not the weights (weights are uniformly 4 = vestigial)\"},{\"type\":\"node\",\"id\":\"f5-trp\",\"kind\":\"CLAIM\",\"label\":\"Routing has three orthogonal knobs: Threshold (T), Recovery (R), Provenance (P); defaultMode is one corner of this space\"},{\"type\":\"node\",\"id\":\"f1-advisor-confidence\",\"kind\":\"FINDING\",\"label\":\"Advisor already emits confidence+threshold+clarifying_question; confidence-first is shipped at Layer 0 for one hub\"},{\"type\":\"edge\",\"id\":\"e-q4-f3\",\"source\":\"f3-learn-assignment\",\"target\":\"q4\",\"relation\":\"ANSWERS\"},{\"type\":\"edge\",\"id\":\"e-f3-f5\",\"source\":\"f5-trp\",\"target\":\"f3-learn-assignment\",\"relation\":\"DERIVED_FROM\"},{\"type\":\"edge\",\"id\":\"e-q4-f5\",\"source\":\"f5-trp\",\"target\":\"q4\",\"relation\":\"ANSWERS\"}]}\nEOF\necho \"appended iter 4\"","workdir":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.worktrees/0063-skilled-router-collapse"},"output":"appended iter 4\n","metadata":{"output":"appended iter 4\n","exit":0,"truncated":false},"title":"cat >> .opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/023-oob-glm-parallel/research/lineages/glm-oob/deep-research-state.jsonl <<'EOF'\n{\"type\":\"iteration\",\"iteration\":4,\"mode\":\"research\",\"target_agent\":\"deep-research\",\"agent_definition_loaded\":true,\"resolved_route\":\"Resolved route: mode=research target_agent=deep-research\",\"newInfoRatio\":0.70,\"status\":\"insight\",\"focus\":\"Confidence-first + learned/adaptive routing (agenda #2+#6): threshold subsumes defaultMode; learn the vocab-to-mode assignment not the weights\",\"findingsCount\":5,\"keyQuestions\":[\"q4\"],\"answeredQuestions\":[\"q4\"],\"noveltyJustification\":\"The (T,R,P) decomposition (F5) and 'learn the assignment not the weights' (F3) are net-new and load-bearing; F1 is confirmatory; F2 is negative-knowledge\",\"ruledOut\":[{\"approach\":\"Confidence-first routing without handoff\",\"reason\":\"Without recovery, the threshold just reproduces run-2's null-with-card verdict (F2); agenda #6 is radical only as the second turn of a two-turn reframe\",\"evidence\":\"iterations/iteration-004.md#negative-knowledge\"},{\"approach\":\"Learn the weights\",\"reason\":\"weight=4 is uniform across the fleet; nothing to learn; real learning target is the vocabulary-to-mode assignment\",\"evidence\":\"iterations/iteration-004.md#negative-knowledge\"},{\"approach\":\"Live in-path weight updates\",\"reason\":\"Breaks router-replay reproducibility, the only executed-evidence harness (F4.4)\",\"evidence\":\"iterations/iteration-004.md#negative-knowledge\"}],\"timestamp\":\"2026-07-18T06:38:00Z\",\"durationMs\":540000,\"executor\":{\"kind\":\"cli-opencode\",\"model\":\"zai-coding-plan/glm-5.2\",\"lineage\":\"glm-oob\"},\"graphEvents\":[{\"type\":\"node\",\"id\":\"q4\",\"kind\":\"QUESTION\",\"label\":\"Does confidence-first + learned routing make defaultMode meaningless?\"},{\"type\":\"node\",\"id\":\"f3-learn-assignment\",\"kind\":\"FINDING\",\"label\":\"Learn the vocabulary-to-mode assignment, not the weights (weights are uniformly 4 = vestigial)\"},{\"type\":\"node\",\"id\":\"f5-trp\",\"kind\":\"CLAIM\",\"label\":\"Routing has three orthogonal knobs: Threshold (T), Recovery (R), Provenance (P); defaultMode is one corner of this space\"},{\"type\":\"node\",\"id\":\"f1-advisor-confidence\",\"kind\":\"FINDING\",\"label\":\"Advisor already emits confidence+threshold+clarifying_question; confidence-first is shipped at Layer 0 for one hub\"},{\"type\":\"edge\",\"id\":\"e-q4-f3\",\"source\":\"f3-learn-assignment\",\"target\":\"q4\",\"relation\":\"ANSWERS\"},{\"type\":\"edge\",\"id\":\"e-f3-f5\",\"source\":\"f5-trp\",\"target\":\"f3-learn-assignment\",\"relation\":\"DERIVED_FROM\"},{\"type\":\"edge\",\"id\":\"e-q