load-bearing or an accident?\"},{\"type\":\"node\",\"id\":\"f1-conflation\",\"kind\":\"FINDING\",\"label\":\"Smell named: routerPolicy fields conflate three orthogonal concerns (T,R,P) across all 7 hubs\"},{\"type\":\"node\",\"id\":\"f2-minimal\",\"kind\":\"CLAIM\",\"label\":\"Minimal router = (T,R,P) triple + vocabulary table; defaultMode/defaultResource/bundleRules/outcomes/tieBreak/ambiguityDelta all deleted or relocated\"},{\"type\":\"node\",\"id\":\"f5-bug\",\"kind\":\"CLAIM\",\"label\":\"defaultMode was never a design knob — it was a documented bug compensating for the missing recovery primitive\"},{\"type\":\"node\",\"id\":\"f5-trp\",\"kind\":\"CLAIM\",\"label\":\"[from iter 4] Routing knob space is (T,R,P)\"},{\"type\":\"node\",\"id\":\"f1-handoff\",\"kind\":\"FINDING\",\"label\":\"[from iter 3] Typed handoff is the missing recovery primitive\"},{\"type\":\"edge\",\"id\":\"e-q5-f1\",\"source\":\"f1-conflation\",\"target\":\"q5\",\"relation\":\"ANSWERS\"},{\"type\":\"edge\",\"id\":\"e-q5-f5\",\"source\":\"f5-bug\",\"target\":\"q5\",\"relation\":\"ANSWERS\"},{\"type\":\"edge\",\"id\":\"e-f5-f1-handoff\",\"source\":\"f5-bug\",\"target\":\"f1-handoff\",\"relation\":\"DERIVED_FROM\"},{\"type\":\"edge\",\"id\":\"e-f2-f5-trp\",\"source\":\"f2-minimal\",\"target\":\"f5-trp\",\"relation\":\"DERIVED_FROM\"}]}\n{\"type\":\"event\",\"event\":\"maxIterationsReached\",\"mode\":\"research\",\"stopReason\":\"maxIterationsReached\",\"run\":5,\"sessionId\":\"fanout-glm-oob-1784347200936-r7aos1\",\"generation\":1,\"timestamp\":\"2026-07-18T06:48:30Z\"}\nEOF\necho \"appended iter 5 + max-iterations event\"","time":{"start":1784348372629,"end":1784348372631}},"id":"prt_f73736e88001MJ5nIEYgnZHd8P","sessionID":"ses_08c9e6f24ffeeO094AtRujB8OZ","messageID":"msg_f73732462001Z7UJpYJKR813Y3"}}
