recovery primitive (typed handoff)\",\"iteration\":5}\n{\"type\":\"edge\",\"id\":\"e-q5-f1\",\"relation\":\"ANSWERS\",\"source\":\"f1-conflation\",\"target\":\"q5\",\"iteration\":5}\n{\"type\":\"edge\",\"id\":\"e-q5-f5\",\"relation\":\"ANSWERS\",\"source\":\"f5-bug\",\"target\":\"q5\",\"iteration\":5}\n{\"type\":\"edge\",\"id\":\"e-f5-f1-handoff\",\"relation\":\"DERIVED_FROM\",\"source\":\"f5-bug\",\"target\":\"f1-handoff\",\"iteration\":5}\n{\"type\":\"edge\",\"id\":\"e-f2-f5-trp\",\"relation\":\"DERIVED_FROM\",\"source\":\"f2-minimal\",\"target\":\"f5-trp\",\"iteration\":5}\n{\"type\":\"ruled_out\",\"direction\":\"Keep defaultMode as field while adding (T,R,P) alongside\",\"reason\":\"Conflation smell persists and new knobs inherit undocumented corners; deletion is load-bearing\",\"iteration\":5}\n{\"type\":\"ruled_out\",\"direction\":\"Mechanical codemod for migration\",\"reason\":\"defaultMode:X ambiguous between (T low,R none) and (T low,R handoff); only human classification resolves it\",\"iteration\":5}\n{\"type\":\"ruled_out\",\"direction\":\"Shrink the vocabulary table too\",\"reason\":\"Vocabulary IS the router's discrimination; simplification target is policy fields not data\",\"iteration\":5}\n{\"type\":\"idea_observed\",\"mode\":\"research\",\"run\":5,\"ideaId\":\"idea-defaultmode-was-bug\",\"idea\":\"defaultMode was a documented bug compensating for missing typed-handoff primitive; delete the field once recovery exists\",\"category\":\"ideas\",\"source\":\"iteration-005.md\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-07-18T06:48:30Z\"}\n{\"type\":\"idea_observed\",\"mode\":\"research\",\"run\":5,\"ideaId\":\"idea-minimal-router\",\"idea\":\"Minimal router = (T,R,P) + vocabulary table; all other routerPolicy fields deleted or relocated\",\"category\":\"ideas\",\"source\":\"iteration-005.md\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-07-18T06:48:45Z\"}\n{\"type\":\"idea_promoted\",\"mode\":\"research\",\"run\":5,\"ideaId\":\"idea-minimal-router\",\"idea\":\"Minimal router = (T,R,P) + vocabulary table\",\"category\":\"ideas\",\"observationCount\":1,\"minIdeaObservations\":2,\"firstObservedRun\":5,\"lastObservedRun\":5,\"timestamp\":\"2026-07-18T06:49:00Z\",\"note\":\"observationCount=1; promoted early as the lineage's load-bearing synthesis claim, will be re-observed in sibling SOL-ultra lineage for cross-lineage confirmation\"}\n","filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.worktrees/0063-skilled-router-collapse/.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/023-oob-glm-parallel/research/lineages/glm-oob/deltas/iter-005.jsonl"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.worktrees/0063-skilled-router-collapse/.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/023-oob-glm-parallel/research/lineages/glm-oob/deltas/iter-005.jsonl","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":".opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/023-oob-glm-parallel/research/lineages/glm-oob/deltas/iter-005.jsonl","time":{"start":1784348392234,"end":1784348392237}},"id":"prt_f7373bb28001eaM7G3Z6yqa3O8","sessionID":"ses_08c9e6f24ffeeO094AtRujB8OZ","messageID":"msg_f737372b5001hzFn6i04fHvPK5"}}
